{"tid":1637573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開咗學就無人出嚟搞事啦！！","createTime":"2019-10-08T04:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T06:37:58.000Z","uid":33495,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc9566542b22c1498bc16fa2681d2b92d092e6f","tid":1637573,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"八月中嗰陣咁講嗰啲去晒邊？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家話撚埋，勇武不休息、不退場啊！<br />\n<br />\n希望和理非繼續努力<br />\n身體上裝、武裝埋自己思想<br />\n唔好上咗裝但搵唔到自己位置<br />\n要退嘅時候就盡快，一早了解定退路<br />\n安全返到屋企就睇新聞檢討得失<br />\n有咩可以做好啲、有咩路係狗唔會入<br />\n<br />\n前線經常可以立功後全身而退<br />\n大家支援完佢地一樣可以平安去食飯<br />\n<br />\n共同進退、光復香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61cc1c0bfbcf907b20f1a1128e384263c8021fb8","tid":1637573,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:37:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果大家覺得資訊混亂 幫手推下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">開設行動台</span><br />\n［連仔入］全部人幫手推 資訊進化論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1637449\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1637449</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"671cca51f64e4eac9898b87dbe51295eee0b7272","tid":1637573,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 十連"},{"pid":"d1697318a64b2b8d70e76f7d997ba02d8241d4ad","tid":1637573,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93aecb50b29fc6b8a9888d43a9565f34e459a260","tid":1637573,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:37:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets